data.description: Welcome home to this two level Colonial in the quaint Willow Oaks neighborhood with no HOA. The full front porch is the first to greet you. It's been a perfect spot to sit and relax on the rocking chairs. There are beautiful hardwood floors on the main level. The sun-filled living room flows into the dining room. The family room is spacious and cozy at the same time. Step out on your deck from the family room. Four good sized bedrooms on the upper level with a loft that has made a great additional area to watch tv, read, and relax. Washer and dryer located on the upper level as well. Convenient shed in the backyard. Riverbend High School District. And check out these recent improvements: In 2020, NEW leaf filter system installed, Pella sliding glass doors, kitchen flooring, fridge, and washing machine. In 2021, NEW stairlift installed. In 2022, NEW dishwasher. In 2023, NEW HVAC, stove, and wheelchair ramp in garage. Call for your tour today!
